quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,13,"Nambi nkuyiona uli naŵaga (Abujahalio) akukanila ni kusyulula?"
  96,14,"Ana ngaakumanyilila yanti Allah akwaona (yaakutenda)?"
  96,15,"Ngwamba! Chisimu naga ngaakuleka, chiitwawuta umbo syapewuwo (pakwaponya ku Moto)."
  98,7,"Chisimu ŵandu ŵaakulupilile nikutendaga yambone, ŵanganyao ni iwumbe yambone nnope."
  98,8,"Malipilo gao kwa Ambuje ŵao chigakaŵe Matimbe Gandamo gasikujilima cha pasi pakwe sulo. Chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo kwa yaka ni yaka. Allah tachanonyela (pakwapochela masengo gao gambone), nombe nao tachinonyelwa Najo (pamalipilo gataachaapa). Yalakweyo ni yamundu jwatan'jogope M'mbujeegwe (Allah)."
  99,4,"Lyele lisikulyo (litaka) lichiŵecheta abali syakwe syosope (sya indu yayatendekwele pachanya pakwe yambone kapena yakusakala)."
  99,5,"Ligongo lyanti Ambuje ŵenu tachililamula lyalakwelyo (kuti liŵechete)."
  99,6,"Lyele lisikulyo ŵandu tachipwilingana ali m'mikutula jakulekangana-lekangana kuti akaalosye masengo gao."
  100,1,"Ngusilumbila hachi syasikuwutuka sili nkupumasika."
  100,2,"Ni syasikoposya moto mu ikotwa mwakwe (pakuwutuka m’maganga)."
  100,3,"Ni syasikwagungumuchila amagongo kumasikusiku."